==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fosseway
<hw>Fosse"way`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of the great
military roads constructed by the Romans in England and other parts of
Europe; -- so called from the <xex>fosse</xex> or ditch on each side for
keeping it dry.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fossick</ent>⟦br⟧
